ComicInfo.Summary:
Time Warp: Part 7 of 8
Mita Celande, Gina and Britanny journey to Dr. Peachbody's era in the far future to find a way to stop him! What they find is a record of his family history dating all the way back to the 20th century. Britanny goes back in time and takes Dr. Peachbody's ancestor to the vet to be fixed! Dr. Peachbody's plans are ruined! At the last moment, he transfers his consciousness to his faithful attack-boy's body to avoid complete annihilation. With his new body, Dr. Peachbody seeks his revenge on Britanny! Concluded in Ninja High School (1986 Antarctic/Eternity) #57.
